HEADWORD: Catoptrical
<hw>Ca*top"tric*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/. See
<er>Catopter</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to catoptrics; produced
