[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Catoptric light</b></col>, <cd>a light in which the rays
are concentrated by reflectors into a beam visible at a
distance.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Catoptrics</ent>⟦br⟧
